d_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-90C","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":15381,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/24\/every-matter-hamd\/","url_meta":{"origin":34634,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Hamd: Every matter begins with praising Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cEvery matter of importance that is not begun with the praise of Allah will be left deficient.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Majah 1894 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Ibn Hajar \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18583,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/28\/believers-drink-well-zamzam\/","url_meta":{"origin":34634,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Zamzam: Believers drink from the well of Zamzam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 28, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, a sign between us and the hypocrites is that they do not drink Zamzam water.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Majah 3061 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u064e\u0651\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0650\u0651 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u