t;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6764,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/20\/ibn-umar-hadith-sunnah-exact\/","url_meta":{"origin":34634,"position":4},"title":"Ibn Umar on Hadith: Following Sunnah exactly as he heard it","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 20, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Ja\u2019far reported: When Ibn Umar, may Allah be pleased with him, heard a tradition from the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, he never added to it and he never fell short of it. Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 4 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u062c\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0631\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6367,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/13\/regret-part-of-tawbah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34634,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Tawbah: Regret is part of sound repentance","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 13, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRegret is part of repentance.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 4252 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631